nodes.text: A Mandalorian of the Mandalorian Clan Eldar pledged his clan to Lady Bo-Katan Kryze and the Mandalorian resistance against the Galactic Empire along with several other Mandalorian factions following the Mission to Mandalore during the Mandalorian Civil War. The Mandalorian leader's support, along with the other Mandalorians, allowed Bo-Katan to take the mantle of Mand'alor.
